<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="substitute-v">substitute <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'sʌbstɪtjuːt/    美 /'sʌbstɪtuːt/  </p>
<p>vt &amp; vi</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(用...) 代替：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You can <strong>substitute</strong> vegetable oil <strong>for</strong> butter in this recipe.
在这份食谱中，你可用植物油代替黄油。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Bill <strong>substituted for</strong> Larry, who was off work.
拉里没有上班，比尔代替了他。</p></div></div>